shift (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Universal document converter with support for PDF, DOCX, HTML, MD, TXT
  * CSS styling support for HTML output
  * PDF compression and page management tools
  * Simple command-line interface: shift document.md --to html
  * Batch processing capabilities

